vinyl2digital - PyPi Package
==================================
**[Vinyl2Digital](https://pypi.org/project/vinyl2digital/) is a Python3 Pip Package for batch rendering multiple audio files using the [Audacity](https://www.audacityteam.org/download/) mod-script-pipe.**

[![PyPI version](https://badge.fury.io/py/vinyl2digital.svg)](https://badge.fury.io/py/vinyl2digital) ![PyPI - Downloads](https://img.shields.io/pypi/dm/vinyl2digital) ![PyPI - License](https://img.shields.io/pypi/l/vinyl2digital) ![PyPI - Python Version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/vinyl2digital)

<img src="readme-gif-1.gif" alt="Demonstration gif" width="950"/>


## Table of content

